    "Roberta Armani is the niece of billionaire fashion designer Giorgio Armani (d. September 2025) and the daughter of his late brother Sergio Armani.",
    "She is a board member of Armani's namesake fashion firm and holds the title of head of global and VIP communications, leading the brand's partnerships with Hollywood stars.",
    "Under the terms of Armani's will, Roberta is entitled to 17% of the net proceeds from the sale or public listing of 45% of the company within five years of Armani's death.",
    "She also inherited some of Armani's shares in eyewear giant EssilorLuxottica."
